# Build output
build/
*.pyc
# v0.62 (Phase 4 teardown): dazzle-bundle.css no longer generated.

# v0.67.95 / #1052: framework asset bundles built by scripts/build_dist.py.
# Previously tracked in git; rebuilt on every release so each ship commit
# added ~3 large binary diffs that buried real changes. Now built by CI
# before the test job (.github/workflows/ci.yml "Build dist bundles" step)
# and by the wheel-publish workflow before twine upload.
src/dazzle_page/runtime/static/dist/dazzle.min.css
src/dazzle_page/runtime/static/dist/dazzle.min.js
src/dazzle_page/runtime/static/dist/dazzle-icons.min.js
# gzipped variants emitted by build_dist.py at the same time:
src/dazzle_page/runtime/static/dist/dazzle.min.css.gz
src/dazzle_page/runtime/static/dist/dazzle.min.js.gz
src/dazzle_page/runtime/static/dist/dazzle-icons.min.js.gz

# Test artifacts
.coverage
htmlcov/
pytest-of-*/
.pytest_cache/
.hypothesis/

# Agent E2E test reports (generated)
**/dsl/tests/reports/

# DAZZLE runtime data
.dazzle/
**/.dazzle/
*.db

# invoice_ops commits its migration history — a project's migrations
# must be version-controlled (see docs/reference/migrations.md).
# Only the versions/ revision files are tracked; other migrations/ runtime
# files (alembic.ini, env.py copies, __pycache__) stay ignored.
!examples/invoice_ops/.dazzle/
examples/invoice_ops/.dazzle/*
!examples/invoice_ops/.dazzle/migrations/
examples/invoice_ops/.dazzle/migrations/*
!examples/invoice_ops/.dazzle/migrations/versions/
!examples/invoice_ops/.dazzle/migrations/versions/**
examples/invoice_ops/.dazzle/migrations/versions/**/__pycache__/
examples/invoice_ops/.dazzle/migrations/versions/**/*.pyc

# Development Docs (legacy)
/devdocs
# Example build outputs
examples/*/build/
examples/*/ui/
examples/*/dnr-ui/

# Node.js
node_modules/
dev_docs/
tmp/

# Vendored/reference repos
alpine/
htmx/

# MkDocs build output
/site/

# Generated API reference docs (built in CI)
docs/api-reference/

